doing the stunts,

1:00:20.701 --> 1:00:21.952
all of it.

1:00:22.036 --> 1:00:23.495
But whatever just happened
wasn't part of it.

1:00:23.579 --> 1:00:25.789
Which is fucking insane, Ron!
For fuck's sake!

1:00:25.873 --> 1:00:27.249
- For fuck's sake?

1:00:27.333 --> 1:00:28.459
That's what you
wanna say to me?

1:00:28.542 --> 1:00:30.127
For fuck's sake?

1:00:38.802 --> 1:00:41.138
- Talk in your regular voice.
- All right.

1:00:41.221 --> 1:00:43.640
No, I've lost it now.
I'm in my head!

1:00:43.724 --> 1:00:46.393
- Who does that?
Who does this to somebody?

1:00:58.447 --> 1:01:00.783
Oh, shit. You okay?

1:01:00.866 --> 1:01:04.620
- Oh, god.
I'm such a fucking idiot!

1:01:04.703 --> 1:01:07.498
What was I thinking?
- What the hell was that, man?

1:01:07.581 --> 1:01:08.916
- You want to know
what the hell is going on?

1:01:08.999 --> 1:01:10.042
- You're goddamn right
I wanna know what's going on.

1:01:10.125 --> 1:01:11.585
- I bought some drugs.

1:01:11.668 --> 1:01:14.380
I sold them to the wrong people.
- What?

1:01:14.463 --> 1:01:17.091
- And Rodrigo got mad at me
and we got into a fight.

1:01:17.174 --> 1:01:19.301
And then, I accidentally
killed him.

1:01:19.385 --> 1:01:20.928
- You did kill Rodrigo.
- Yes.

1:01:21.011 --> 1:01:22.304
- I told you
he fuckin' killed him.

1:01:22.388 --> 1:01:24.765
- And that necklace.
That necklace was his necklace.

1:01:24.848 --> 1:01:26.683
I'm a horrible person.

1:01:26.767 --> 1:01:28.852
