you call the cops right now.

1:01:37.152 --> 1:01:38.904
You call the fuckin cops.

1:01:38.987 --> 1:01:41.365
- Senor Wilcox!

1:01:41.448 --> 1:01:43.033
- Oh, shit.

1:01:43.117 --> 1:01:44.785
- My nephew Rodrigo's body
washed up

1:01:44.868 --> 1:01:47.287
