like a chicharone.

1:02:03.429 --> 1:02:06.306
- Snap out of it!
- I can't! It's over!

1:02:06.390 --> 1:02:07.975
- Listen to me,
motherfucker.

1:02:08.058 --> 1:02:10.644
This is why men shouldn't be
left in charge of anything!

1:02:10.727 --> 1:02:13.397
My career is just now
becoming the thing

1:02:13.480 --> 1:02:16.442
that I have worked
my entire life towards!

1:02:16.525 --> 1:02:18.902
And I'm not dying because
of you, you fucking idiot.

1:02:18.986 --> 1:02:21.071
- We're all gonna die!

1:02:23.824 --> 1:02:26.034
- Oh, shit.
- What the fuck, man?

1:02:26.118 --> 1:02:28.120
- Everybody gotta
calm the fuck down!

1:02:28.203 --> 1:02:30.330
- They're all blanks.

1:02:30.414 --> 1:02:32.332
- Hey. Hey. Hey.
- Don't hit me.

1:02:32.416 --> 1:02:34.543
- I'm not gonna hit you.
Look.

1:02:34.626 --> 1:02:37.463
When I first walked through
that door, you told me.

1:02:37.546 --> 1:02:38.755
You said, "Kevin--"

1:02:38.839 --> 1:02:40.966
You said an action hero
is not in here.

1:02:41.049 --> 1:02:43.469
You said it's not in here.
- Uh-huh.

1:02:43.552 --> 1:02:45.179
- You said that it's here.

1:02:45.262 --> 1:02:47.055
It's in your heart, man.

1:02:47.139 --> 1:02:49.600
You know, clearly,
you done made some mistakes.

1:02:49.683 --> 1:02:51.518
And one of those mistakes
involved murderin'

1:02:51.602 --> 1:02:53.270
the nephew of some kind
of drug lord.

1:02:53.353 --> 1:02:55.147
- Oh, god.

1:02:55.230 --> 1:02:56.815
I killed him!

1:02:56.899 --> 1:02:58.984
- I'm not tryin' to
fuckin' upset you, man.

1:02:59.067 --> 1:03:01.195
Listen.
I know that you know.

1:03:01.278 --> 1:03:04.490
