for their shit.

1:03:16.919 --> 1:03:19.213
You go out there
and you tell the truth, man.

1:03:19.296 --> 1:03:21.256
Tell the fucking truth.

1:03:21.340 --> 1:03:23.967
Say Rodrigo's death--
say it was an accident.

1:03:24.051 --> 1:03:26.220
Say it was a fucking accident.
And give 'em--

1:03:26.303 --> 1:03:28.180
Give 'em this.
Here.

1:03:28.263 --> 1:03:29.431
You give 'em this,

1:03:29.515 --> 1:03:31.141
say you wanna make
things right.

1:03:31.225 --> 1:03:32.267
- I wanna make it right.
- That's all you gotta do!

1:03:32.351 --> 1:03:33.936
Say I wanna make it right.
I'm sorry.

1:03:34.019 --> 1:03:35.437
I fucked up.
- I fucked up.

1:03:35.521 --> 1:03:37.481
- I wanna tell the truth.
- I wanna tell the truth.

1:03:37.564 --> 1:03:39.358
- That's it!
- I don't wanna make a mistake.

1:03:39.441 --> 1:03:40.484
- Okay, listen.

1:03:40.567 --> 1:03:43.111
All you gotta do
is be the action hero

1:03:43.195 --> 1:03:46.657
that you wanna see
in the world.

1:03:46.740 --> 1:03:48.951
- Thank you.

1:03:49.034 --> 1:03:50.869
Thank you.

1:03:50.953 --> 1:03:52.454
- Tell the truth, man.

1:03:58.168 --> 1:03:59.586
- That was amazing.

1:04:05.259 --> 1:04:06.593
- Amigos!

1:04:06.677 --> 1:04:07.719
Amigos.

1:04:07.803 --> 1:04:09.221
Peace. Peace.

1:04:09.304 --> 1:04:10.722
- Paz.

1:04:10.806 --> 1:04:12.057
- Paz. Paz.

1:04:12.140 --> 1:04:13.058
- Paz. Paz. Paz. Uh...

1:04:13.141 --> 1:04:15.686
- Shit, it's
actually working.

1:04:15.769 --> 1:04:18.105
Kevin, did you just
save our lives?

1:04:18.188 --> 1:04:20.440
- No. I just know
that being the hero

1:04:20.524 --> 1:04:22.985
means ownin' up
to your mistakes.

1:04:23.068 --> 1:04:26.029
